trans-unit.source: Represents a configuration element that specifies a privacy notice used in `wsFederationHttp` binding.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Configuration.PrivacyNoticeElement"></xref> class.
Applies the content of a specified binding element to this binding configuration element.
Gets the <xref href="System.Type"></xref> object that represents this custom binding element.
A <xref href="System.Type"></xref> object that represents this custom binding type.
Copies the content of the specified configuration element to this configuration element.
The configuration element to be copied.
Creates a new a custom binding element object based on the setting of this configuration element.
A custom <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElement"></xref> object whose properties are based on the setting of this configuration element.
Initializes this binding configuration element with the content of the specified binding element.

Gets a <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection"></xref> instance that contains a collection of <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty"></xref> objects that can be attributes or <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement"></xref> objects of this configuration element.

A <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection"></xref> instance that contains a collection of <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationProperty"></xref> objects that can be attributes or <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement"></xref> objects of this configuration element.
Gets or sets the URI at which the privacy notice is located.
The <xref href="System.Uri"></xref> at which the privacy notice is located.
Gets or sets the version of this privacy notice.
An integer that specifies the version of this privacy notice.
